      "content": "i know i should talk to my doctor but i can't get an appointment for like two weeks and i'm literally losing my mind from exhaustion. i just wanted to know if they actually interact in a bad way or if it's just a precaution? i mean they're both just sleep aids, right? it seems like it would just be more effective.",
